quran[3]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,46,"Kuwa huba inay la kulmi Rabbigood, iyo inay Xaggiisa u soo laaban (Qiyaamada)."
  2,47,"Ilmahii Israa’iilow! Xusuusta Nicmad- deyda aan idiinku nicmeeyey, iyo inaan idinka doortay dadkii (waqtigiinna Anigoo idiin soo diray Rusul oo idinku soo dejiyey Kutub oo idinka yeelay boqorro)."
  2,48,"Iska jirana Maalin marka aysan nafi wax u tareyn naf kale, oo aan laga aqbaleyn shafeeco, lagana qaadanayn madax furasho, loona gargaareyn."